                                            scalable for years to come.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <div class="d-flex mb-4">
                                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success fs-3"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex-grow-1 ms-3">
                                        <h4 class="h5 fw-bold mb-2">Community & Support</h4>
